About Us
Utah Retirement Systems (URS) provides benefits for state and other Utah public employees.  The Retirement Office administers pension and retirement savings plans.  PEHP specializes in medical, dental, life, and other benefits.
In addition to excellent career opportunities, we offer great benefits!
Health Benefits

Medical & dental
Vision
Life and long-term disability

Retirement Benefits

Participation in the URS Public Employees' Retirement System.
Immediately eligible to participate in a 401(k) and/or 457 plan.

Time Off Benefits

13 paid vacation days
11 paid holidays
Paid sick leave

Additional Benefits

Flex Plan (tax savings account)
On-site exercise facility
Employee fitness program














