Planholder's list information



My company's contact for this Planholder's list

                        The contact for the Planholder's list is the person whose contact information will be listed for any listing this company places. In addition, this contact will also receive update notifications for any Planholder's list that the company is subscribed to.
                        

Listing my company on the Planholder's lists

                        To list a company for a particular Planholder's list, open the tab for the Planholder's list that you would like the company to be listed under (Sub contractor or Prime contractor) and click the 'Add my company to this Planholder's list' link. To complete the listing process, you need to accept the release company information dialog for placing a listing. No subscription is necessary to list a company on a Planholder's list. Conversely, to remove your company from the list, click on the 'Remove my company from this Planholder's list' link.
                        

Subscribing to a Planholder's list

                        To subscribe to a particular Planholder's list, open the tab for the Planholder's list that you would like to subscribe to (Sub contractor or Prime contractor) and click the 'Subscribe' button. Some Planholder's lists cost to view, and the price will be listed in the text right above the 'Subscribe' button. To complete the subscription, terms and conditions need to be accepted. Note, that this button will be replaced with a view of the listings if this company has already subscribed to this list.
                        








